did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.physdesc: Correspondence, Diaries, Financial Records, Printed Materials, Publications, Reports.
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Collection development records, vendor correspondence, and permanent records of the library of the New York State College of Agriculture and Life Sciences. Also old Mann Library plaque.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Collection development records, vendor correspondence, and permanent records of the library of the New York State College of Agriculture and Life Sciences. Also old Mann Library plaque.
